  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is undertaken to investigate whether relaxing music therapy before, during and
      after laparoscopic cholecystectomy has any effect on pain, PONV or fatigue and level of
      stress as measured by Cortisol and C reactive protein.

      Patients will be scored according to those endpoints 1 and 3 hours after surgery and on day 1
      and 7 post-OP.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
